o control the drift requires that only rear-wheel drive and some all wheel drive vehicles be used. Typically, drift drivers use inexpensive and lightweight Japanese vehicles such as the Nissan 240SX and its Japanese counterpart, the Silvia, but American cars have been used in competition recently as well.#drifter#drift\u00b7ed#drift\u00b7ing#drifts#driftyby Mr Drift September 03, 200612751 Get a drifting mug for your brother Manafort.5driftingunknownA really entertaining way to ruin your tires.Some dude just went drifting by me in a cloud of smoke and hit a wall, man!#crashing#missing walls#tokyo#drift king#funby XomegaX October 06, 200910649 Get a drifting mug for your mother-in-law Yasemin.6driftingunknownSomething homeless people do from town to town.Did you see that homless guy drifting last night?#drift#240sx#racing#stupid#motorsport#wannabeby BMWguru November 19, 20106631 Get a drifting mug for your papa G\u00fcnter.7driftingunknownMaking the car slip laterally by means of oversteering. Possible with a RWD vehicle. Some people try this with FWD cars as well by driving in Reverse. Its aptly defined as \"Controlling your car when it is in uncontrolable zone\"US competed in the Drifting Grand Prix with a Pontiac GTO and were knocked out before the round of 15.by LedVTECin August 20, 200413977 Get a drifting mug for your guy Callisto.Categories\ud83d\udeac Drugs\ud83d\ude4f Religion\u26bd\ufe0f Sports\ud83c\udf93 College\ud83c\udfa7 Music\ud83c\udf46 Sex\ud83c\udf70 Food\ud83d\ude4b\ud83c\udffd Name\ud83d\udcac Internet\ud83d\udcc8 Work123Next \u203aLast \u00bb\u00a9 1999-2019 Urban Dictionary \u00aeadvertise\u00a0terms of serviceprivacy\u00a0dmca\u00a0removehelpActivityAlphabetical listdriftbeerdrift bitchdrift cardrift charmdrift compatibledrift drivedrifteddrifted ondrifterdrifter (Noun)Drifter&apos;s stitchdriftgirldrift handleDriftillerationdriftindriftingDrifting in someones wakedrifting napdrifting on a memorydrifting prettydrifting sack of shitdrifting tur